'''聖詹姆斯區'''位於[[巴貝多|巴貝多]]中西部，與[[聖安德魯區_(巴巴多斯)|聖安德魯]]、[[圣迈克尔区|圣迈克尔区]]、[[聖彼得區_(巴巴多斯)|聖彼得區]]、[[聖托馬斯區_(巴巴多斯)|聖托馬斯區]]等區相鄰。該處被譽為富豪及名人的後花園，亦是渴求日光浴的人的避風港<ref>{{cite news |title=Property in the Caribbean: Welcome to Barbados |author= |first=Anna |last=Tyzack |authorlink= |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/property/overseasproperty/7258740/Property-in-the-Caribbean-Welcome-to-Barbados.html |agency= |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |publisher= |location= |isbn= |issn= |oclc= |pmid= |pmd= |bibcode= |doi= |id= |date=19 February 2010 |page= |pages= |at= |accessdate=24 June 2010 |trans-title= |quote= |ref= |archive-date=2013-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116190603/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/property/overseasproperty/7258740/Property-in-the-Caribbean-Welcome-to-Barbados.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

